('ONET-FOOD_SCIENTISTS_AND_TECHNOLOGISTS', 'source_onet_food_scientists_and_technologists', 'Food Scientists and Technologists', 'Food Scientists and Technologists is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Use chemistry, microbiology, engineering, and other sciences to study the principles underlying the processing and deterioration of foods; analyze food content to determine levels of vitamins, fat, sugar, and protein; discover new food sources; research ways to make processed foods safe, palatable, and healthful; and apply food science knowledge to determine best ways to process, package, preserve, store, and distribute food.', ARRAY['Applications Scientist','Corporate Food Scientist','Crop Advisor','Dairy Bacteriologist','Enologist','Fermentation Scientist','Flavorist','Food and Drug Research Scientist','Food Engineer','Food Preservation Scientist','Food Processing Scientist','Food Safety Auditor','Food Safety Regulatory Manager','Food Safety Scientist','Food Scientist','Food Technologist','Formulator','Hybrid Corn Breeder','Hybrid Technologist','Postdoctoral Research Associate (Postdoc Research Associate)','Product Development Scientist','Product Development Specialist','QC Scientist (Quality Control Scientist)','Quality Food Expert','Research Chef','Research Scientist','Scientist','Swine Nutritionist','Swine Technician (Swine Tech)']::text[], ARRAY['Food Scientists and Technologists','Applications Scientist','Corporate Food Scientist','Crop Advisor','Dairy Bacteriologist','Enologist','Fermentation Scientist','Flavorist','Food and Drug Research Scientist','Food Engineer','Food Preservation Scientist','Food Processing Scientist','Food Safety Auditor','Food Safety Regulatory Manager','Food Safety Scientist','Food Scientist','Food Technologist','Formulator','Hybrid Corn Breeder','Hybrid Technologist','Postdoctoral Research Associate (Postdoc Research Associate)','Product Development Sci